<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Best Small Hotel in Mexico's Largest City Among Mexico City's tall downtown buildings, sits one of the best hotels I have ever stayed at. Only 45 rooms, but situated on an extremely quiet street, this hotel has wonderfully colorful room decor, comfortable accomodations, private baths and is convenient to tourists and businessmen alike. Close to Alameda Park, the Zocalo and other attractions and nightlife- the Hotel New York is situated in an extremely ideal location. A small but cozy restaurant is often quite busy and each room has a 27 inch color television. I highly recommend this hotel while visiting Mexico City. 
